sharedPost.text:
✨ FREE PHOTOSHOOT ✨

I’ve got a brand-new lighting setup and camera and I’m looking for models of all ages to practice with! 📸

👉 What you’ll get:
All usable photos will be uploaded into a private online gallery. If you’d like to purchase any images, they’ll be £10 each – but there’s absolutely no obligation to buy.

To take part:
🌸 Like this post
🌸 Message me with a recent photo & age
🌸 Follow my page
🌸 Share this post 

Can’t wait to create some magic with you ✨

Also shared to Instagram - Shay Hill Photographer

items.text:
**Szukam modelki na zasadzie TFP  Gliwice/Katowice ( Śląsk )**

 

   Poszukuje kobiety w **wieku od 30 **lat nie koniecznie z doświadczeniem pozowania,  na zasadach Tfp mieszkającej w Gliwicach lub okolicach Zabrze czy Katowice najdalej. Posiadam na wyposażeniu mini studio z kilkoma tłami oraz lampami. Mam również duży wybór kostiumów i gadżetów do wykorzystywania. Główny motyw do kobieta: Piękna i drapieżna! Sama sesja trwa przeważnie od 1,5h do 2h w zalezności od motywów.

 

- Kobieta mafii 1930

- Sensualne

- klasyczne

 

W tym roku będę również realizować swój projekt mini serialu osadzony w 1940 roku. Szyje też do niego większość kostiumów.

 

**Zapraszam na stronę Facebook Łukasz Magiera – Fotografia**

 

Więcej informacji na Priv

✨ BIG CREATIVE ANNOUNCEMENT! ✨ 

I’m beyond excited to officially introduce One World Studios HQ — a brand NEW multi-room creative content space in Baltimore, MD built for visionaries, storytellers, and creators of every kind.

Here’s what awaits you:

• 🎥 All-White Photography & Video Room – the perfect blank canvas.
• 🎙️ Podcast & Live Stream Studio – ready to record and broadcast.
• 🎬 Fully Equipped Live Talk Show Set – with a backstage walk-on experience.
• 📺 4K Multi-Camera + Switcher – professional-grade production tools.
• 🎞️ Film/Movie Series Design Space – bring your cinematic vision to life.
• 🏢 47,000 SQ FT of Open Space – or simply a clean, inspiring environment to create your vision.

One World Studios HQ was designed for creators who want an affordable, exclusive, and welcoming environment to produce their next big project.

Additional amenities include:

🍻 On-site brewery with food options
🅿️ 24-hour parking
💡 Stocked furniture, lighting, wireless & wired mic systems
☕ Cozy hospitality nook
…and much more.

📩 Inquire Today: info@OneWorldStudiosHQ.com

💡 We’ll even help you create a custom budget or payment plan that fits your production needs.

Your vision deserves a space where it can truly shine—let’s build it together at One World Studios HQ.

Feel free to REPOST and SHARE to someone who perhaps need help bringing their vision/brand/product to Life.

items.text:
✨ Extras wanted for a rave scene! ✨

We’re shooting a nightclub scene for our experimental short film Falling Forward, Slightly tomorrow in Nørrebro, and we’d love some extra energy on the dance floor.

- Nørrebro

- 19:00–22:30 (just a few hours)

- Unpaid, but short, fun, and a chance to be part of a unique artistic project.

Falling Forward, Slightly is an experimental film about a swimmer, a fighter, and a dancer whose stories collide. It’s a passion project where we explore movement, sound, and atmosphere instead of dialogue.

We’ve already been filming some beautiful scenes (see stills below), and now it’s time for the rave!

If you want to join us and be part of the vibe, send me an email to **luciasanmiguel94@gmail.com**

**STATISTER I ALDEREN 35-55 (ALLE TYPER) SØGES TIL REKLAMEFILMSOPTAGELSER - LØNNET**

Spoiled Productions søger **15 statister** til en dags reklamefilmsoptagelser for et bolig-interiør firma i et studie på Refshaleøen, København.

**Hvornår**: D. 1. eller D. 2. oktober i nogle timer (specifikt tidspunkt følger).

**Hvor**: Refshaleøen, København.

**Løn**: Efter aftale.

Hvis du er ledig de to datoer, og kan være med et par timer den dag vi lander på, må du meget gerne sende en mail til astridjuliane@gmail.com med:
* Billede
* Navn + alder
* Kontaktinfo (email + telefonnumer).

Det kræver ingen erfaring - bare lysten til at være med!

Glæder mig til at høre fra dig:)

*NB Jeg besvarer henvendelser løbende de næste par dage.

items.text:
Vi søger fire erfarne skuespillere til en kortfilmoptagelse, som finder sted den 13. oktober på Helsingør rådhus. Projektet omfatter ca. 8 timers optagelse, og vi søger to mænd og to kvinder i alderen 50-100 år til roller som politikere. Produktionen er et skoleprojekt for Folketinget, med fokus på at fremme unges deltagelse i politik. Filmen vil ikke blive offentliggjort, men delt med jer efterfølgende. Lønnen er biografbilletter🤗

Hvis det lyder som noget for dig, kan du skrive en mail

Kontakt: Mortenmorkjensen@gmail.com

❄️ EXCLUSIVE CASTING: Professional Ice Skaters (Solo & Duo) ❄️

🖇Apply Now :   https://risingstars-talents.com/ice-skating-jobs/?utm_source=reg-FB-shl

✨Auditions, casting calls, gigs, careers, jobs, contracts for dancers, circus acts, musicians, pianists, singers, vocalists, ballroom, salsa couples for cruises, hotels, festivals. International Talents booking agency Rising Stars.

Dream opportunity! ✨ We are looking for talented solo and duo ice skaters ready to captivate audiences with stunning performances.

🌟 What’s included:

✔️ Contract start: October- November 2025

✔️ High salary

✔️ Contract with extension option

✔️ Accommodation & flights covered

✔️ Legal work permit & full support

✔️ Unique chance to perform on an international stage

📩 Don’t miss your chance to shine on the ice - apply now via the link!

items.text:
**CASTING-AUFRUF – UGC-Videodreh für Immobilienprojekt in Heidelberg // Donnerstag 25.09.2025**
 
Drehort: Heidelberg // Bahnstadt

Drehtag: 25.09.2025 - 10.00 Uhr
 
Geplanter Drehzeitraum: halber Drehtag (4–5 Stunden)
Schauspielhonorar: 500 € pauschal
Was wir drehen:

Für unseren Kunden, einen Immobilienunternehmen aus Hamburg, produzieren wir 25 kurze UGC-Videos (User Generated Content) für Social Media & Online-Ads. Die Videos sind authentisch gesprochene Clips, die direkt in die Kamera eingesprochen werden – klar, sympathisch, ruhig.

Skriptlänge pro Video: 40–60 Sekunden, ein Teleprompter ist vor Ort – keine Auswendiglernerei notwendig.
 
Gesucht werden:
* 1 Schauspielerin & 1 Schauspieler
* Alter: 28–40 Jahre
* Look: authentisch, gepflegt, urban-professionell – ein natürlicher „Young Professional“-Vibe (Think: Start-up, Immobilienberater, Creator mit Vertrauensausstrahlung)
* Sprache: Hochdeutsch, sichere Sprechweise, gute Artikulation
* Erfahrung mit Kamera & Social Media Ads von Vorteil, aber keine Voraussetzung
Über uns:

Wir sind die IMMO 4.0 GmbH, ein Performance-Marketing-Unternehmen aus Heidelberg.

Wir entwickeln Marketingkampagnen für Immobilienvertriebe, Bauträger und Kapitalanlageprodukte im DACH-Raum – und setzen dabei bewusst auf echtes, greifbares Storytelling mit professionellem UGC-Content.

Das bieten wir Dir:
* 500 € Pauschalgage
* Teleprompter + eingespielte Crew vor Ort
* Styling & Text-Input durch uns (kein Kostüm notwendig, clean/professionell reicht)
* Reelfähige Referenz für Deine Mappe
* Zusammenarbeit mit erfahrenem Videoteam in lockerer, produktiver Atmosphäre

Bewerbung:

Bitte sende uns bis asap Deine Bewerbung mit:
* 2–3 aktuellen Bildern oder Showreel
* Kurzprofil (Name, Alter, Standort)
* Optional: Link zu Instagram / Agenturseite / Eigenen Reels
* Betreff: „UGC-Videodreh Heidelberg – Vorname Nachname“

Bewerbung bitte per WhatsApp an: +49 172 7042469

(Phillip Kirillov - IMMO4.0 GmbH)

Hinweis:

Die finalen Produktionen erscheinen im Rahmen einer Online-Marketingkampagne für den Bereich Kapitalanlage-Immobilien. Seriös, hochwertig, glaubwürdig.

Wir freuen uns auf Deine Bewerbung – let’s create!

Dein Team von IMMO 4.0 GmbH

items.text:
Hi @everyone 

Long shot but, thought I try. 

**LONDON - LEAD ROM-COM ACTRESS **

I want to try to make **10 episode vertical rom-com**, and looking for collaborative **actress 25-40** who would like to be a co-lead in the series. 

I have never made vertical drama project so this is just a fun, collaborative experience. 

The character is **typical rom-com lead, tall, attractive, native English-accent preferable but, not essential.  **

The episodes are about 1-2 mins long so, I believe we could film all 10 of them over one weekend, if not one whole day.

Mostly for **YouTube/TikTok and experience (unpaid). **

If you're interested, please DM me, and we can talk more. :)

🎬 CALLING ALL WEB SERIES CREATORS! 🎬

Bullz Global Entertainment is now seeking fresh, innovative, and budget-friendly web series concepts for production! 🌟

Do you have a gripping story, unique characters, or a binge-worthy idea? This is your chance to showcase your talent on a global stage! 🌍📺

🎯 We’re looking for:

✨ Original, engaging, and out-of-the-box concepts

✨ Stories that can attract international audiences

✨ Formats that are budget-friendly yet powerful

✨ Narratives adaptable across different cultures and languages

📌 Genres We’re Open To:

🎭 Drama | 😂 Comedy | 💕 Romance | 🔮 Sci-Fi | 🕵️ Thriller | 👨‍👩‍👧 Family/Youth | 🌏 Socially Relevant Stories | 🎬 Anthologies

📢 For more details & updates, join our creator groups:

💬 WhatsApp: https://chat.whatsapp.com/E7fOOVwKxMz4i8E4vPzwbk?mode=ac_t

💬 Telegram: https://t.me/+hEFgvwvXhQxlMjA9

📩 For questions or queries:

✉️ Email: contactus@bullzglobalentertainment.com

📱 WhatsApp: +91 9150063204

💬 Or DM me directly on Facebook or WhatsApp for more details.

🌎 Open to creators worldwide. All submissions must be in English.

📌 T&C Applied

🚀 Let’s create the next global binge-worthy series together!

sharedPost.text:
Hi,
I’m an actress based in the North West of England. I’m looking for projects, short films and feature films to audition for. I don’t have a showreel or a cv but I am trained in musical theatre and singing. I also attended college for performing arts too. My main type of acting has been on stage but I’m looking to broaden my horizons with screen acting. My main Instagram is therealbabyghoul and my acting Instagram is Ashleymarshperformer
If you have any projects please either message me or drop a comment. 
Thanks,
Ashley

items.text:
🚨URGENT CASTING CALL🚨

Project Title: SIO: Origins
Production Company: Museboxx M&F
Location: Darbyshire???? TBA (UK-based production)
Deadline: Urgent

Role: Co-Starring Leads – Names TBA
We’re casting for two dynamic male actors to take on a co-starring leading roles in our upcoming production, SIO: Origins, part of the larger SIO universe. The roles are emotionally charged and physically demanding, featuring performance across acting, dance, singing, and occasional stunt choreography. For these roles, We do have places for the characters to appear on the final episode of SIO:Echoes of the SIX - which has been airing throughout this year online. And to be a part of other SIO series', including live performances and other Muaeboxx projects.

Character Traits & Requirements:

• Sexuality: Gay & Bisexual
• Age: 26-28
• Height: 5ft 7 to 6ft
• Performance Abilities: Singer, Dancer, Acting and Rap
• Comfortable of doing own Stunts
• Comfortable with doing Gymnastics
• No piercings/jewelry

• Must be available for Live Performances

Previous experience in emotionally intense roles is a bonus

Payment & Contract:
Budget is currently being finalised. Payment details will be discussed at a later stage and confirmed in actor contracts. This will be a credited role with potential for expanded involvement in future series.

To Apply:
Send an email to museboxxmfcasting@outlook.com to send the following: Submit headshot, showreel (if available).
Audition scripts and details will be provided upon application.

If you have any issues with contacting the email above, please don't hesitate to contact our other email below - wintersxperia@gmail.com

More details about the projects will be discussed throughout the Audition process.

🎅🏼 CHRISTMAS CASTING 🎅🏼

We're on the lookout for a jolly, warm-hearted Father Christmas to bring festive magic to life at one of Liverpool’s top attractions this November & December!

✨ The Role: You’ll be the star of our magical grotto experience, meeting families, chatting with children, and spreading Christmas cheer. A twinkle in the eye, a hearty "Ho Ho Ho", and a love of all things festive are a must!

📍 Location: Prescot, just outside of Liverpool 
📅 Dates: Select dates throughout Nov & December (22 dates)
💰 Competitive day rate + full costume and training provided

📧 To apply, please send a short intro, recent photo/headshot, and any relevant experience to Info@LaughingBulldogEvents.co.uk with the subject line "Father Christmas Casting - Liverpool".

Do pierwszego odcinka 20. sezonu serialu "Gliniarze", realizowanego w Warszawie, wciąż poszukuję mężczyzny do roli:

1. Gangster (38) – postawny gangus, łysy, wydziarany, z prawem jazdy (!!!)

Data: 30. września
Stawka: 350 zł netto

Chętnych Panów zapraszam do wysyłania zgłoszeń na adres: casting.outset@interia.pl

W tytule maila proszę o wpisanie nazwy postaci.

W treści maila proszę umieścić:
* linki do swoich materiałów video
* aktualne zdjęcie
* wiek, wzrost, wagę
* informacje o dotychczasowym doświadczeniu 
* oraz nr telefonu do kontaktu

Nie zwracamy kosztów dojazdu i noclegu.

items.text:
Ruszamy z kolejnym (już 20.) sezonem serialu „Gliniarze” realizowanego w Warszawie!!!

Do pierwszego odcinka tego sezonu poszukuję mężczyzn do następujących ról:

1. Tarik Dubajew (52) – przestępca z klasą w typie biznesmena, wschodnia aparycja, lekki wschodni akcent.

[PŁATNE]

Do etiudy Łódzkiej Szkoły Filmowej poszukujemy dziecięcego aktora głosowego do roli narratora. Do nagrania jest tylko kilka kwestii voice-overu, więc całość zajmie ok. 3-4h. Oferujemy symboliczne wynagrodzenie.

Kogo szukamy?
Aktora w wieku 6-10 lat z subtelnym, gładkim i lekko tajemniczym głosem. (referencja w linku)

Kiedy?
Kwestie planujemy nagrać w okolicach 30 września. (Dokładny termin do dogadania)

Gdzie?
ul. Targowa 61/63, Łódź 

Zgłoszenia proszę przesyłać na maila kusz.krzys@gmail.com z załączoną próbką głosu i numerem telefonu.
Zapraszam do kontaktu. :)

items.text:
how relevant are certificates gotten from Alison acting courses? and also how can I get an agent as a professional singer ?
I've been trying to get an agent but it's so difficult...why?
Do you have to pay to any agent to get featured in their website?

topComments.text:
Not sure on Alison Acting courses… ‘professional’ means you generally get paid for what you do, at which point the only reason to really get an agent is to fill up your work calendar a but more.

Should never pay an agent upfront, any reputable agent would take a cut per contract they get you.

Ever thought of doing weddings? Even though it might not be your thing, wedding singers can usually earn anywhere between £200-£350 in a weekend. 
Same with tribute bands and/or cruises…cruises tend to pay a bit more.

Jeg står med ansvaret for en natklub i København, og i forbindelse med Halloween leder jeg efter nogle søde og engagerede mennesker, der har lyst til at være en del af vores festlige (og uhyggelige) team.

Vi søger folk, der kan agere “skræmmere” og være med til at skabe den helt rigtige stemning. Det drejer sig om tre aftener: 30., 31. oktober og 1. november.

Der er naturligvis tale om lønnet arbejde

items.text:
Kortfilmen “Babyshower” søger kvindelige statister.

Hvor: Thurø
Hvornår: 6.-9. november fra 9.00 til ca. 16.00

Til kortfilmen “babyshower” skal vi bruge kvinder i alderen 25-35 år. Du skal have erfaring med at spille skuespil og improvisere. 

Optagelserne foregår på Thurø i perioden 6.-9. november, og vil ligge idagstimerne i tidsrummet 9.00-16.00. Jobbet er ulønnet, og man skal selv sørge for transport til lokationen. Der vil være forplejning under optagelserne.  

Med i din ansøgning skal der være et selftape på max 2. min. med en impro-øvelse som lyder som følger:

Du ankommer til et babyshower med en gave til hovedpersonen, som hun pakker op, men ikke ser ud til at kunne lide.

fortæl nu hovedpersonen, hvad den ting kan, og hvorfor lige præcis dén er så super fed at have som nybagt mor.

Du bestemmer selv om du vil gøre scenen dramatisk eller humoristisk.

Tænker du det er dig vi kan bruge, skal du sende os en ansøgning. Den skal indeholde følgende oplysninger:

Navn
Alder
Billede
Kontaktinfo
Selftape

Alt dette sender du i en e-mail til MANFilm@outlook.com og gerne så hurtigt som muligt.

Bedste hilsner
Malene 
Statistkoordinator - BABYSHOWER

topComments.text: Gør det noget man er 42 😇 hvis man elsker skuespil
Gør det når man er 13 hvis man elsker skuespillere når man tager makeup på ligner man en større end hvad man er en på 15 16 år

message.text:
🔥 BULLET RUSH PREMIERE 🔥

We’re at the Plaza Theatre putting the final touches on the Bullet Rush World Premiere — and trust us, this is one night Atlanta will NEVER forget! 🎬✨

From the red carpet lights to the heart-pounding action on screen, this premiere is pure adrenaline. Tickets are flying — and once they’re gone, they’re gone!

🎟 Don’t miss history in the making. Grab your tickets TODAY on Eventbrite or through the link in bio. October 19, 2025 is YOUR night to #FeelTheRush.

https://www.eventbrite.com/e/bullet-rush-movie-premiere-tickets-1684936322899?aff=oddtdtcreator

Awesome job to my brother
Tobias Armand for this dope slick video!

#BulletRush #AtlantaPremiere #RedCarpetEvent #MoviePremiere #OpenGateStudios #ArmourVisionStudios

# 🎬 **NAGRANIA KRAKÓW **🎬

Do realizacji ciekawego filmu na jeden z największych kanałów YouTube w Polsce poszukujemy osoby chętnej wziąć udział w projekcie. Zadaniem aktora będzie odegranie krótkiej sceny z elementami improwizacji. 
## 🔎 **Kogo szukamy?**
* Mężczyzna w wieku 25-50 lat
* Łysa głowa (nie wymagana, ale mile widziana 🙂)
* Dystans do siebie
* Swoboda przed kamerą (doświadczenie mile widziane, ale niekonieczne)
## ℹ️ **INFORMACJE**
* Lokalizacja: Kraków
* Termin: 17.09.25
* Czas trwania: 1 godzina

** Jesteś chętny? – odezwij się w wiadomości prywatnej, a prześlę więcej szczegółów! **

items.text:
🎭 **CASTING CALL – New Australian Play in London** 🎭

We are casting **four roles** for an exciting new Australian play, *The Beat of the Bronzewing*, which will have a **showcase reading at the Hen & Chickens Theatre, Islington, on November 12th**.

🌪️ **About the Play:**
When Peggy shows up at Lorraine’s shack in dead-end tropical Australia, she brings an irresistible offer: a one-way ticket out of there. But with a cyclone looming and old wounds resurfacing, can Lorraine be convinced she has nothing to lose?

✨ Longlisted for the **Theatre 503 International Playwriting Award 2025**, *The Beat of the Bronzewing* explores the lives of three women in remote Australia, grappling with toxic femininity, domestic abuse, and rural isolation. Set against an evocative tropical landscape, the play is a gripping story of friendship, fear, and survival.

👩‍🎤 **The Team**
✍️ Writer & Producer: Charlotte Churcher
🎬 Director: Chloe Cattin
🤝 In partnership with the Australian Women’s Club London

📅 **Key Dates**
* **Auditions:** October 8th (12–5pm) at the Old Red Lion Theatre, Angel, Islington (alternative arrangements available if needed)
* **Rehearsals:** Sunday 9th November (10am–6pm) & Wednesday 12th November (from 2:30pm)
* **Showcase:** Tuesday 12th November at Hen & Chickens Theatre

💷 This is a **volunteer opportunity** with a £50 contribution towards expenses.

👉 To apply, please complete the form in full.
https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSch7cgoIcL_f8KVARDySxKb7eM4Q2gpUXLmmDLPhppJCDDR-w/viewform

Scottish accent preferred, not essential Retregnka Rehearsals on 9th November (10am (10am-6pm) and 12th November (2:30 to 7pm). Please submit via the Google form link provided. This sa volunteer opportunity. All actors will be given £50 pounds for expenses.'

🌟🎤 Boyband Stars Wanted! 🎤🌟
We’re creating a brand-new live show celebrating the greatest boybands of all time — from Backstreet Boys, NSYNC, Take That, Westlife, Boyzone and Blue through to One Direction (and many more)...

We’re looking for UK-based male singers (18–35) with:
✨ Fantastic vocals (lead & harmonies)
✨ Rhythm, stage presence & confidence &movement
✨ Team spirit — able to shine solo and blend in a group
✨ Availability for rehearsals & touring
.
This is a full-scale production with dazzling choreography, mind-blowing medleys, mash-ups, and the biggest anthems of the boyband era...
.
📩 To apply, email: talent@superstar-productions.com
.
(Please include your details, headshot & performance clips

We’re creating a brand-new live show celebrating the greatest boybands of all time — from Backstreet Boys, NSYNC, Take That, Westlife, Boyzone and Blue through to One Direction (and many more)...

We’re looking for UK-based male singers (18–35) with:
✨ Fantastic vocals (lead & harmonies)
✨ Rhythm, stage presence & confidence &movement
✨ Team spirit — able to shine solo and blend in a group
✨ Availability for rehearsals & touring
.
This is a full-scale production with dazzling choreography, mind-blowing medleys, mash-ups, and the biggest anthems of the boyband era...
.
📩 To apply, email: talent@superstar-productions.com
.
(Please include your details, headshot & performance clips

🚨URGENT CASTING CALL🚨

Project Title: SIO: Origins
Production Company: Museboxx M&F
Location: Darbyshire???? TBA (UK-based production)
Deadline: Urgent

Role: Co-Starring Leads – Names TBA
We’re casting for two dynamic male actors to take on a co-starring leading roles in our upcoming production, SIO: Origins, part of the larger SIO universe. The roles are emotionally charged and physically demanding, featuring performance across acting, dance, singing, and occasional stunt choreography. For these roles, We do have places for the characters to appear on the final episode of SIO:Echoes of the SIX - which has been airing throughout this year online. And to be a part of other SIO series', including live performances and other Muaeboxx projects.

Character Traits & Requirements:

• Sexuality: Gay & Bisexual
• Age: 26-28
• Height: 5ft 7 to 6ft
• Performance Abilities: Singer, Dancer, Acting and Rap
• Comfortable of doing own Stunts
• Comfortable with doing Gymnastics
• No piercings/jewelry

• Must be available for Live Performances

Previous experience in emotionally intense roles is a bonus

Payment & Contract:
Budget is currently being finalised. Payment details will be discussed at a later stage and confirmed in actor contracts. This will be a credited role with potential for expanded involvement in future series.

To Apply:
Send an email to museboxxmfcasting@gmail.com to send the following: Submit headshot, showreel (if available).
Audition scripts and details will be provided upon application.

If you have any issues with contacting the email above, please don't hesitate to contact our other email below - wintersxperia@gmail.com

More details about the projects will be discussed throughout the Audition process.

Want to be part of a real theatre ensemble and gain hands-on acting experience?

ACT Ensemble Theatre Company is looking for new members to bring A Christmas Carol to life on stage this December.

Train like a professional actor as you rehearse with an experienced director, work alongside a creative team, and perform for a live audience. Singing and movement classes are included to help you build your skills and confidence.

Auditions are now open for this advanced training course.

items.text:
Hi everyone . I’ve not posted in groups in a long time . I took a break from acting full time almost six years ago when I nearly lost my little girl nine times in one year  to an illness. 
I spent those six years, training , making connections and friends. Some directors, producers and writers from the likes of Netflix , Warner Bros, Lionsgate etc and some known actors . I wrote scripts that have now been sold to Lionsgate directors and being read by Pierce Brosnan, Samuel L Jackson and many more . 
I changed my whole outlook on acting and the industry and Instead for the last six years it’s been my only goal to help as many actors as I possibly can . I’ve self funded features to help get as many actors and crew seen as I can , always circulating new actors and new crew every film. 
I spent the last six years building an acting curriculum and opened The Foundry Acting Studio after I not only exceeded spotlight approval by over three times but the studio is also SAG recognised too and soon to be other organisations. 
I’ve had actors come to my class for three or four weeks and leave other major schools they were training at for three to four years. 

I offer in person. Online and one to ones. Which all information can be found on the page or by messaging The Foundry Page. 

I get it trust me . New acting classes , new showreel offers , new headshot specialists . There’s always doubt and to be honest what I’ve noticed a lot recently in groups is a lot of hate , a lot of abuse and I’ve seen people being attacked left , right and centre in this industry for posting a headshot or looking work. This industry is an absolutely amazing place , if we all pick each other up. So please keep your hate to yourself . All you’re doing is commenting and people are never going to work with you if you’re rude , foul mouthed or ignorant . 

So yes I understand people being weary of new things but I’m hoping we’ve answered a lot below and again. Like the biggest schools out there.  I am spotlight approved , but I’m also the only independent studio in the U.K. to be SAG recognised and soon to be more . This proves legitimacy. 

So if you’re an actor or starting acting and you want real training , check out the post below. Also if you’re a good person , support other actors and pick people up rather than putting people down. Then you’ll fit perfectly. 

Again . Help each other . Pick each other up. Support each other and be kind to each other . Show new actors that the industry can be a wonderful place . 

Also …. We are the only acting studio making full industry professional feature films and we cast from our students. 

So message us now ….. hope to meet a lot of you soon and keep being fantastic and pushing for that dream

sharedPost.text:
🎬 The Foundry Acting Studio 🎬

Train. Work. Belong.

Where world-class coaching meets real screen credits.

At The Foundry, we don’t do hype, we do results. 

📚Our coach is an internationally trained actor who paused his own career for five years to build a rigorous, modern curriculum from the ground up. (For the record: the world’s best acting coaches aren’t always front-of-camera stars, coaching and acting are different crafts. Ours happens to do both, and he’s now stepping back on set while leading this programme.)

✅️Verified. Recognised. Trusted.
 • Spotlight-approved training (and then some). When Spotlight reviewed our curriculum, it exceeded their requirements by roughly three times.
 • SAG-recognised. We’re one of very few independent UK studios to be both Spotlight-approved and SAG-recognised, with more professional bodies in progress.
 • Our curriculum has been reviewed by established actors, directors, producers and casting directors. Their feedback is consistent: “This is the calibre you’d expect from a major, prestigious franchise school.”

✅️Training that turns into work
 • We own our kit: RED cinema cameras, top-tier lenses, pro-grade sound, the works. No hired “showreel days.”
 • We produce our own professional features and shorts and cast from our students.
 • Speaking roles guaranteed in our in-house features/shorts for committed students who complete the pathway, because the goal isn’t just growth; it’s getting you working.

✅️Accessible. Supportive. Serious.
 • £100 every four weeks for in-person classes or online classes.
 • We also offer one-to-one's intensives to go deeper, faster.
 • We welcome beginners, returners and working actors, and all different backgrounds. Whether you’re on a pension, benefits, full-time or part-time work, we’ve designed this to be accessible and judgment-free. No nepotism. No gatekeeping. Just craft.

🎥Why actors choose The Foundry Acting Studio 
 • Curriculum: far beyond the minimum, Spotlight-approved ×3.
 • Pathways: SAG-recognised, with additional organisations pending.
 • Industry connection: active relationships with professionals who’ve worked across Netflix, Warner Bros., Lionsgate, FX, HBO, and more.
 • Outcomes: high-level training plus on-set experience and speaking roles in our productions.

📢What actors are saying
 • “Four weeks here taught me more than two years at one of the North’s biggest schools.”
 • “After one 1-to-1 session, I left the class I’d attended for 18 months, the difference was night and day.”
 • “I moved from another ‘top’ school after four weeks at The Foundry, no comparison.”

📚What you get with us📚
 • High-level curriculum which has taken five years to perfect.
 • Spotlight-approved curriculum, SAG-recognised pathways.
 • Guaranteed speaking roles in our in-house shorts/features (for students who complete the pathway).
 • Professional sets with RED cameras, cinema lenses, and pro sound.
 • £100/4 weeks, in-person + online, with optional one-day intensives.
 • A community that’s welcoming, motivating and serious about your future.

✨️Ready to forge your craft and your career?✨️

Join The Foundry Acting Studio.

Contact us for more information 
📧 Info@thefoundryactingstudio.com

items.text:
Kristian Beck - Kölsche Tön! Seid ihr bereit für den „❤️KÖLSCHEN❤️“ Musikgenuss?

In diesem Clip präsentiere ich euch - elf kurze Hörproben meines "Special Albums" - Kölsch trifft Schlager. Ein Mix aus rockigen, poppigen, karnevalistischen und weihnachtlichen Klängen!

Egal ob beim Feiern im Karneval oder beim gemütlichen Beisammensein – hier ist für jeden etwas dabei!

items.title: Cześć !🥳

items.text:
📣 CASTING – SERIAL "NA SYGNALE" 📣
Szukamy mężczyzn w wieku 19–23 lata do epizodycznej roli AKTYWISTY w serialu Na sygnale.
🗓 Data zdjęć: 29 września 2025 (poniedziałek) 📍 Miejsce: Warszawa – Falenica 💰 Stawka: 250 zł / dzień zdjęciowy (umowa, przelew)
Wymagania:
sprawność fizyczna,
brak obcego akcentu (wymóg produkcji),
mile widziane długie włosy,
pełna dyspozycyjność w dniu zdjęć (godzina rozpoczęcia nieznana),
najlepiej osoby z Warszawy i okolic (brak zwrotu kosztów dojazdu),
osoby, które długo nie brały udziału w planie serialu "Na sygnale".
Opis sceny:
Postać aktywisty – wylewa farbę na karetkę i zostaje zatrzymany.
Jak się zgłosić?
Wyślij e-mail na adres: statysci.nasygnale@gmail.com 📌 Tytuł maila: NA SYGNALE – AKTYWISTA 29.09
W treści zgłoszenia podaj:
imię i nazwisko,
wiek + wzrost,
miejscowość zamieszkania,
telefon kontaktowy,
aktualne zdjęcia (obowiązkowo!).
⏳ Na zgłoszenia czekamy do jutra do godziny 10:00. Spośród zgłoszeń wybiera II reżyser. Wybrana osoba zostanie powiadomiona SMS-em.

⏰ Ostatnie 2 tygodnie na zgłoszenie ! ⏰
Zapraszamy na III Festiwal Piosenki Online „Zmierzając do Ciebie. Zmierzając do Marzeń” 2025 🎶

➡️ Formularz zgłoszeniowy: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScFUYHbuGbJi9S3Uf--O-S7wPxRkIrhsMPktGBHC9OvBv5C_w/viewform
➡️ Regulamin: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nF0pi0ffAbU2bvzePyVFt_dD87blIRG_/view

Co wyróżnia nasz festiwal ?
🎁 Każdy uczestnik dostanie niespodziankę pocztą – nie PDF, ale prawdziwą paczkę!
🏆 Laureaci otrzymają puchary i medale, które wyślemy prosto do Waszych domów.
🎤 Wystarczy nagrać 2 piosenki i podesłać linki z YouTube.
👥 Brak ograniczeń wiekowych – solista, duet czy zespół – każdy jest mile widziany.

📅 Zgłoszenia przyjmujemy tylko do 30 września 2025 !
👉 Nie zwlekaj – dołącz i przeżyj emocje, kiedy nagroda trafi w Twoje ręce. 💖

items.title: ZGŁOSZENIE: III FESTIWAL PIOSENKI ONLINE ”ZMIERZAJĄC DO CIEBIE. ZMIERZAJĄC DO MARZEŃ” 2025
items.summary:
⏰ Ostatnie 2 tygodnie na zgłoszenie ! ⏰
Zapraszamy na III Festiwal Piosenki Online „Zmierzając do Ciebie. Zmierzając do Marzeń” 2025 🎶

➡️ Formularz zgłoszeniowy: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScFUYHbuGbJi9S3Uf--O-S7wPxRkIrhsMPktGBHC9OvBv5C_w/viewform
➡️ Regulamin: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nF0pi0ffAbU2bvzePyVFt_dD87blIRG_/view

Co wyróżnia nasz festiwal ?
🎁 Każdy uczestnik dostanie niespodziankę pocztą – nie PDF, ale prawdziwą paczkę!
🏆 Laureaci otrzymają puchary i medale, które wyślemy prosto do Waszych domów.
🎤 Wystarczy nagrać 2 piosenki i podesłać linki z YouTube.
👥 Brak ograniczeń wiekowych – solista, duet czy zespół – każdy jest mile widziany.

📅 Zgłoszenia przyjmujemy tylko do 30 września 2025 !
👉 Nie zwlekaj – dołącz i przeżyj emocje, kiedy nagroda trafi w Twoje ręce. 💖

 Immediate start – contract ends in October

 Work in a 5-star environment

(Apply ASAP—positions may fill quickly!)

CEO

7:58 AM (2 hours ago)

to me

Dancer & singers job advertisement and schedule

 Last Summer Jobs – Dance & Sing Entertainer Under the Greek Sun! 

(EU citizens & non-EU residents with a valid EU residence permit welcome)

This is your last chance to land a paid summer job in paradise!

Palmera Entertainment is hiring for the final dancer and singer positions at 5★ resorts in the beautiful Greek Islands.

If you love the stage, sun, and sea – this job is for you.

 Available Roles for male & female 

            •     Entertainer ( kids, Sports )

 • Dancer / performer 

 • Singer / Performer

 Location: 5★ Hotels – Greek Islands

 Contract Dates: August 1st – October 31st, 2025

 Swiss employment contract

 Net Salary: from €800/month + commissions ( depends on positions& experiences)

 We Offer:

 •  Free accommodation

 •  Full board (3 meals/day) + drinks included in the main restaurant 

 •  Free transfer from airport to hotel

 •  Free internet & laundry service 

 •  Free uniforms

 •  Free rehearsals and show training

 •  €200 travel bonus (paid at contract end)

 •  Full insurance (accident, pension, social)

 •  Extra bonuses for merchandising promo

 •  An unforgettable summer experience

 Typical Workday (~8 hrs):

 • Morning: 09:45–12:30 – Activities or kids club

 • Afternoon: 14:45–17:00 – Sports, games, or creative sessions

 • Evening: 20:00–23:00 – Mini disco, shows, social dancing

 •  5-6 performances/week, 1 hour per show

 •  Mini Disco: 2–3 times/week (20:15–21:00)

 •  Main Break: 17:00–20:00

 •  Rehearsals: As needed (usually midday)

Schedules can vary slightly by hotel and concept – flexibility is key.

Hi Everyone, 

We are currently looking for freelance dance and drama artists (aged 18-30) based in and around Derbyshire to take part in a well-known musical theatre show! - Reveal happening soon!
 
Auditions will be free to attend, and the chosen cast will be given fair compensation for all rehearsals and performances. This opportunity is aiming to provide valuable experiences to those of you who are struggling to find a way into the industry.
 
Rehearsals will commence in February 2026 on Tuesdays, Wednesdays and Thursdays from 10am-3pm in Chinley (High Peak); and shows are currently set to take place on the 19th, 20th and 21st March 2026 at New Mills Art Theatre.
 
If you are interested in taking part and want to find out more information, please sign up to our mailing list below: https://forms.gle/5FJyLNDdafigtWRn9 
 

 
I am also on the lookout for local people that have experience being a light and/or sound operator. These roles will be paid £14.50 per hour and will be needed for 40 hours between the 9th and 21st March. 
Potential to work full-time at New Mills Art Theatre after successful show.
 
Please email me at molly.sodenfreeth@act2.org.uk if you have any further questions.

Come along and join us at Ilkley Playhouse for this amazing event starting on September 25th and until 27th…
PS I’m directing one of the EIGHT short plays but don’t let that put you off :-)

items.text:
# CASTING CALL: JOIN OUR ACTING PODCAST

When a group of actors sit around a table and use their spoken words to portray characters all going on an adventure together, that's called a tabletop roleplaying game (TTRPG). Our gaming group plays a variety of tabletop roleplaying games and publishes the audio as a podcast. Example famous ttrpg podcasts: Critical Role, The Adventure Zone, etc. We react as our character to the scenario presented by the game master. We respond to challenges, overcome obstacles, make jokes and laugh with our fellow acting friends. Would you enjoy acting in-character for a podcast audience? Join us.

# When we play:

Weekends. Both European and American time zones. Joining us doesn't commit you to every weekend. Instead, we pick games we want to try and sign up for those calendar spots.

# How long we play / what it’s like:

Our members sit at their microphones for four hours talking their way through an adventure using their words and laughter to entertain each other. We use theater of the mind, saying out loud how far away targets are instead of looking at combat maps on a screen. The recordings are high quality, and we air the audio as a podcast. Don’t worry, we don’t publish our names or faces.

# System played:

We get to learn and play a different tabletop roleplaying game (ttrpg) system each session. There’s no financial burden to you. The systems are either free to everyone or we were sent a free promotional copy from its creator.

# Oneshot or campaign:

Both. Like a traditional campaign, we repeatedly meet familiar non player characters (NPCs), facing challenges and experiencing long term character growth. We play our same character for a year. Our characters start at low power in January, grow to epic max fighting strength by December, then retire. Like a oneshot, each individual episode opens with a beginning to its plot, and the exploration of its story ends after four hours.

# Game Mastering (GMing):

We rotate so that everyone is invited to be a player and a game master if they want. The GM gets to pick which ttrpg we play that weekend. If you find a fun ttrpg you want to try, you can sign up as the GM and be confident that there will be players excited to play with you. If you prefer to be a player every time that’s cool, too. Our members don't have to GM ever if they want a break from it. Getting to pick how often you GM really helps relieve burnout. GM as often as makes you happy.

# You can vibe check past games:

We're on itunes, spotify, youtube, and all the podcast apps. Our cast rotates. Skip around and listen to snippets from a few episodes to see which of our members you want to play with first. The episodes aren't all great, but we have fun together. This isn't a job. It's a hobby, a way to relax and laugh meeting new people who slowly over time become lifelong friends. It's okay to miss games; you aren’t expected to be present for every session. The opt-in format naturally minimizes table trouble because you can see who’s signed up to GM and play in a game before you join it, and can pick dates that have people you’re looking forward to playing with.

# Joining:

To join, email us at FirebreathingKittensPodcast at gmail dot com and tell us about your equipment. Our minimum requirement is 24 bit audio (not 16 bit). If you don’t know what 24 bit audio means that’s not a problem, the new members tab of FirebreathingKittensPodcast dot com has an equipment section that explains what all the microphone words mean with pictures and videos. We welcome members of all experience levels and will train you. The new members tab also has info about our format and answers to frequently asked questions. Minimum age 21 years old. We reply to all emails from people who have 24 bit audio within three days with a support agreement for you to sign, and then will guide you through character creation and train you how to record great audio.

topComments.text: The opt in schedule is the best part. Play when you're available, don't worry about when you're not.

items.text:
Casting Call 한국인 배우를 찾습니다

Location: Greater Vancouver Area
Production Type: Student / Non‑Union
Format: Narrative short 
Shooting Date: November 13-15 2025 (3 consecutive days)
Compensation:  Catering, Crafty, imdb credit
Safety: Child-actor compliant set: guardian required on set for minor.
PRODUCTION COMPANY : Vancouver Film School

Please submit resume, headshot, and demo reel (if applicable) to       Onlyforadaysf@gmail.com                  and indicate which role you’d like to be considered for. The selected actors will be sent sides with self-tape instructions.

Logline
A lonely Korean girl meets a magician hired to play her father for one day. A lie that becomes the most magical memory of her childhood.

Genre
Family Drama

Tone & Keywords
Warm, gently magical, grounded realism, themes of memory, identity, belonging, immigrant family, quiet humor.

ROLES
1) YUNSEUL / 윤슬 (Lead)
Female, 5-12, Korean. Sensitive, curious, and quietly lonely after moving to Canada. Hair‑twisting habit reveals anxiety. a believer who finds wonder in small things. The emotional heart of the film.
Language: English (primary), Korean (bonus).
Guardian: Parent/guardian required.

2) MAGICIAN (Lead)
Male, 25–35, Korean/Korean American. Witty on the surface, quietly lonely underneath. hides wounds behind jokes and tricks. A father‑for‑a‑day who is changed by Yunseul’s trust.
Language: English (primary), Korean (bonus).
Notes: Open to learning simple magic.

3) JUNGHEE / 정희 (Lead)
Female, 25–35, Korean/Korean‑descent. Protective, practical, and loving; carries guilt over the story she tells her daughter about the absent father. Hires the Magician out of fierce love and hope.
Language: English (primary), Korean (bonus).

4) CHUY (Supporting)
Male, 25–35, Korean/Korean‑descent. Playful “uncle” energy, eases the mood with quick humor. Quietly honest protects the boundary of magic so it keeps its power.
Language: English (primary).

**Paid Studio Gig – Surrey, BC (1–2 days, max 7 hrs/day)**

Hey Vancouver actors! We’re producing a batch of short videos for our brand (YouTube, Reels, TikTok, Facebook) and are looking for a confident on-camera presenter to record with us at our Surrey studio.

**What it is:**
* 1–2 studio days, max **7 hours per day**

‼️NORTHWEST BIPOC ENTERTAINERS‼️

We are actively seeking talented BIPOC performers to bring beloved characters such as; Princess Tiana, Mulan, Mirabel, Jasmine, Moana, iconic Korean figures and more to life through engaging and authentic performances.

To our company representation matters! We are committed to celebrating the rich cultural heritage of these characters embodied by casting performers who reflect their backgrounds. Whether you're an experienced entertainer or a passionate newcomer, if you have a love for storytelling, performance, and creating magical moments for audiences of all ages, we invite you to join us in inspiring the next generation through inclusive and empowering portrayals.

Please PM Ever Enchanted Events or email everenchantedevent@gmail.com with a headshot, CV and a little about yourself and your background🥰⭐️

📢Volunteers Wanted - Videographers! Liverpool Mystery Event📢

CAJ Productions is looking for 2 more reliable volunteers to help with a one-off mystery stunt in Liverpool City Centre on Saturday 20th September 2025.

It's part of a brand-new UK theatre tour coming in 2026, and this will be one of our headline public marketing stunts. 

The role is simple, but really important:

. Filming the event (reactions) on a phone (2 people required)

What you'll get:

. Travel expenses covered

. Be part of an unusual, exciting event that's going to get a lot of attention

. Something different to talk about (and looks great on a CV for anyone in events, film, or theatre)

If you're free, reliable, and up for being part of something mysterious and fun, drop me a message here or comment below and I'll share the details.

Thanks! 

Charlie

🎃Halloween acting job opportunity🎃

🎃 Join the Cast of Halloween at Winstanley Park! 👻✨

We’re searching for fun, energetic, and family-friendly performers to bring the magic of Halloween to life at Winstanley Park’s half-term events this October!

Event Details:
 • 📅 Event Dates: 25th – 31st October
 • ⏰ Times: 10:00am – 4:30pm daily
 • 💷 Run Rate: £1050 for the full event

Rehearsals (attendance required):
 • 🗓️ Rehearsal: 17th October
 • 🗓️ Dress Run: 21st October

What We’re Looking For:
 • Friendly, engaging performers who love interacting with children and families
 • Ability to stay in character and create a magical, seasonal atmosphere
 • Great storytelling and improvisation skills
 • Previous experience in theatre, children’s entertainment, or immersive events is a plus
 • ✅ Must hold a valid DBS check

What You’ll Get:
 • A competitive run rate
 • The chance to create unforgettable Halloween memories for families
 • A supportive, creative team environment in the beautiful Winstanley Park

👻 Whether you’re a mischievous witch, a cheeky pumpkin sprite, or a friendly ghost, we want to hear from you!

How to Apply:
📩 Please send:
 • Your CV
 • A 30-second video of you telling a short ghost story
to: RegallyRoyalParties@yahoo.com

Audition Day (in-person):
📅 26th September
⏰ 4:00pm – 6:00pm

🎬 Ever wondered what it’s really like behind the scenes of landing a role on Wednesday?

👉 Watch the full clip to hear how it all unfolded – from missed cues to that unforgettable call saying “You booked it.”
What’s the most stressful audition experience you’ve ever had? Share in the comments 👇@followers

# 🎬 **NAGRANIA KRAKÓW **🎬

Do realizacji ciekawego filmu na jeden z największych kanałów YouTube w Polsce poszukujemy osoby chętnej wziąć udział w projekcie. Zadaniem aktora będzie odegranie krótkiej sceny z elementami improwizacji. 
## 🔎 **Kogo szukamy?**
* Mężczyzna w wieku 25-50 lat
* Łysa głowa (nie wymagana, ale mile widziana 🙂)
* Dystans do siebie
* Swoboda przed kamerą (doświadczenie mile widziane, ale niekonieczne)
## ℹ️ **INFORMACJE**
* Lokalizacja: Kraków
* Termin: 17.09.25
* Czas trwania: 1 godzina

** Jesteś chętny? – odezwij się w wiadomości prywatnej, a prześlę więcej szczegółów! **

items.text:
Casting Call – Mandlig skuespiller/statist søges

Vi er et hold på seks studerende fra VIA Film & Transmedia i Aarhus. I forbindelse med et skoleprojekt samarbejder vi med designer Fie Nielsen og hendes studie, Fjör Studio, om branding af en ny tøjkollektion.

Kollektionen udforsker, hvad det vil sige at være mand i dag, og leger med udtryk, der udfordrer de traditionelle forestillinger om styrke, følelser og identitet.

Vi søger en mand i alderen 17–30 år, ca. 180 cm høj, almindelig af bygning og med tøjstørrelse small–medium.

Praktisk info
 Optagelserne finder sted i Skanderborg
 Mandag den 22/9
 Kl. 09.00–17.00

Projektet er frivilligt, men vi sørger selvfølgelig for mad, drikke, transport – og en sjov oplevelse samt muligheden for at få et spændende projekt på CV’et.

Kontakt Fredrik på (+45) 2285 1519 eller 354549@via.dk, hvis du er interesseret. 

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

items.text:
Casting Call – Voice Actors (Ulønnet)

Hej alle,

Vi er et hold fra Masterclass på Potemkin – Den Jyske Filmskole, som er i postproduktion på et spændende projekt. Derfor søger vi nu stemmeskuespillere til to roller.

Logline:

En håbefuld, men overset filminstruktør får chancen i en branche styret af sequels og profit – og må vælge mellem at gå på kompromis med sine værdier eller med sin karriere.

Vi søger:

 • Kvindestemme – til at udlevere en Robertpris (kort ceremoniel replik - tænk "And the Oscar goes to..."). Alder er underordnet.

 • Mandestemme – til rollen som producer (kort telefondialogscene). Alder underordnet, da det er stemmen vi søger, men vi søger i omfanget af 25-39 år. 

Praktisk:

 • Projektet er ulønnet, men alle medvirkende bliver krediteret i filmen.
        • Lydoptagelsen vil foregå i Potemkins lydstudie på Fredens Torv 3A, Aarhus C 8000.

Er du interesseret? Send mig en mail på simonthomaslange@gmail.com med en kort besked, eventuelt som lydoptaglese, så får du flere detaljer :)

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

topComments.text: Hej Simon, jeg har sendt jer en mail. (-:

items.text:
**🎬 CASTING-AUFRUF – UGC-Videodreh für Immobilienprojekt in Leipzig // 26.09.2025**

📍 **Drehort:** Leipzig

📅 **Drehtag:** Freitag, 26. September 2025 – Start: 10:00 Uhr

⏰ **Dauer:** ca. 4–5 Stunden (halber Drehtag)

💶 **Honorar:** 500 € Pauschalgage

**🔹 Was wir drehen:**

Für unseren Kunden – ein Immobilienunternehmen aus Leipzig – produzieren wir **15 kurze UGC-Videos** (User Generated Content), die für **Social Media & Online-Ads** eingesetzt werden.

Die Clips bestehen aus **authentischen Monologen**, die direkt in die Kamera gesprochen werden: **klar, sympathisch, ruhig und professionell**.

* Skriptlänge: 40–60 Sekunden pro Clip
* Teleprompter ist vor Ort (kein Auswendiglernen nötig)
* Fokus: **seriöse, glaubwürdige Darstellung**

**🔹 Wen wir suchen:**

👤 **1 Schauspielerin (weiblich)**

* Alter: 25–35 Jahre
* Look: gepflegt, urban, authentisch-professionell (z. B. „Young Professional“-Vibe – denkbar wären Start-up-Gründer, Immobilienberater, Creator mit Vertrauensausstrahlung)
* Sprache: Hochdeutsch, **klare Artikulation** und sichere Präsenz vor der Kamera
* Erfahrung mit Social Media Ads ist ein Plus, aber **keine Voraussetzung**

**🔹 Über uns:**

Wir sind die **IMMO 4.0 GmbH**, ein Performance-Marketing-Unternehmen aus Heidelberg.

Unser Schwerpunkt: **Marketingkampagnen für Immobilienvertriebe, Bauträger und Kapitalanlagen im gesamten DACH-Raum**.

Wir setzen auf **echtes Storytelling und professionell produzierten UGC-Content**, um seriöse Projekte authentisch darzustellen.

**🔹 Das bieten wir Dir:**

* 500 € Pauschalgage
* Teleprompter & eingespielte Crew vor Ort
* Styling-Hinweise & Text-Input durch uns (kein Kostüm notwendig, clean/professionell reicht)
* Reelfähige Referenz für Deine Mappe
* Zusammenarbeit mit erfahrenem Videoteam in lockerer, produktiver Atmosphäre

**🔹 Bewerbung:**

Bitte sende uns so schnell wie möglich Deine Bewerbung mit:

* 2–3 aktuellen Bildern oder Showreel
* Kurzprofil (Name, Alter, Standort)
* Optional: Link zu Instagram / Agenturseite / eigenen Reels

👉 Betreff: **„UGC-Videodreh Leipzig – Vorname Nachname“**

👉 Bewerbung per WhatsApp an: **+49 172 7042469 (Phillip Kirillov – IMMO 4.0 GmbH)**

items.text:
CASTING CALL

We’re looking for a female actor to join us this December for our RAPUNZEL pantomime (school tour). 

We’re casting either of the following parts, with our existing performer playing the opposite role. 

- Rapunzel (lead)
- Gothel (villain)

Last year was our best selling tour - but we hope to beat that this year! Because it’s schools, the shows are weekday mornings and early afternoons, so you’ll have your evenings and weekends free. The performances are in the Norfolk, Suffolk and Cambridge area. 

We’re currently offering a minimum of £870 - which will go up as we get more bookings in + travel expenses. 
The tour spans from 1st - 19th December 2025. 
Aiming to start weekly rehearsals asap - in Hunstanton (PE36). These are unpaid but we keep them as flexible as possible.

This will be our thirteenth panto tour, and we’ve built up a good name in the area, with schools booking us year after year (even before we announce the title!) We pride ourselves on being a warm, friendly, but professional company.

If interested, please get in touch for further details - either by a PM on here, or via email - purple-dreams@hotmail.co.uk - I’m looking forward to hearing from (some of) you 🙂

Many thanks
Tobias Nicholls
Creative Director 
Purple Dreams Productions

items.text:
INTENSE CRIME DRAMA - SHORT (PAID)

1-day shoot in London (UK) for 2nd week in October 2025 (date tbc)

(For actors based in the London area).

 

Summary: A night of heavy drinking ends in a deadly contest between newfound besties - a fearless Nigerian gangland enforcer and a trigger-happy European gunman.

 

This project is Episode #0 of ‘Brave Hunter in Ghost City’  - introducing a new African story world and some of its main characters. ** **

 

MALE LEAD: to play fearless gangland enforcer.  Black African, 25-45, Lagos accent, 5’6”+, athletic physique with good fitness and conditioning. Stage combat training. Flat rate of £300 for 15 hours.

 

MALE LEAD: to play trigger-happy gunman. White European,  35-45, 5’ 6”+, 85kg-100kg,  powerful physique with good fitness and conditioning. Stage combat training. Flat rate of £300 for 15 hours.

 

SUPPORTING MALE: to play dead gangster. White European, 35-45, 5’ 6”+, 80kg-100kg. Half a day of shooting for £150 for 7 hours.

 

You will need professional experience playing character roles on Stage, Film or TV. Please send in a cover letter, your CV with headshot and your showreel to Davina Brown at k2Filmworks@gmail.com

🎭ADVERT CASTING BRIEF🎭

Looking for the below Actors:

* 1 x Businesswoman, white, 40s, fit, redhead (banker vibes) - send a 30 sec video speaking Posh English Accent 

* 1 x Businessman, white, 40s, blonde (banker vibes) - Send 30 sec video speaking posh English accent 

* 1 x white woman to be the Driver, 20s (non-speaking)

* 5 x Japanese men, 30s – 60s (attractive, good looking) - send a 30sec video reacting and “sounding” Japanese

* 1 x Japanese woman, 20s (non-speaking)

* 2 x White men, late 40s (successful businesspeople, but outdoorsy types. Strapping men) - send a 30 sec video speaking Good Australian accent. – “Yeah mate!”

* 1 x Black man (Driver), 40s/50s

* 2 x Indian women, 1 x 30s/40s and 1 x 50s. English speaking - send 30sec video speaking English in authentic Indian/Mumbai accent

* 1x Indian man, 30s. English speaking. - send a 30 sec video speaking English in authentic Indian accent
* 2 x Arab men, 30s & 40s (groomed facial hair – beards don’t have to be long or bushy – the current trend is quite short and well-shaped) - send a 30 sec video speaking English but with a natural Saudi / Arab / Gulf accent

* 2x Arab men (non-speaking)

* 2 x Italian men, 40s and 50s (dashing or handsome) - send 30sec video speaking good Italian.

* 1 x Italian woman, 30s (striking or attractive) - send a 30sec video speaking good Italian 

* 1 x Portuguese man 40s (darker-haired – maybe a curl, warmer/olive-skinned, maybe dense facial hair… a Mediterranean vibe) - send a 30sec video speaking Portuguese and English

* 1x Black South African man, 40s (charismatic businessman vibe, the air of trust and success) - Send a 30sec video speaking good English

* 1 x Portuguese woman, 30s + 1 x Black South African woman, 30s  (non-speaking)

* 1 x French man, white, 40s (mischievous, urban, effortlessly stylish, and slightly romantic… a sense of refinement, wit, and nonchalant charm) - send a 30sec video in Good French accent “C’est magnifique!”

* 1 x Chinese man 50s/60s (professional-looking guy. Well-groomed) - send a 30sec video in a distinct Chinese accent

- Speaking Role: Rate is R4000
- Non-Speaking Role: Rate is R2000

DEADLINE: WEDNESDAY (17/09/2025) at 5pm. 

Thank you 
LJ Talent Casting 💫

message.text: Manoj Kumar is celebrated as one of the most iconic and respected actors of Indian cinema. Known affectionately as “Bharat Kumar”, he earned this title for his patriotic roles that inspired generations. With his dignified screen presence, soulful performances, and deep sense of social responsibility, he portrayed characters that upheld values of integrity, sacrifice, and love for the nation. Beyond his acting, he is admired for his direction and storytelling, which combined entertainment with strong messages of unity and moral courage. His work continues to be a benchmark for meaningful cinema in India.Rose’s #####Teapot…..👍👍🍻🥂🎬🎬🏅🏅🏆🏆

items.text:
Hello all, this is another post for a different student film happening on Auraria Campus. I am not involved in this one, I am posting to this group for the producer since he is not on Facebook. So if you are interested in this one please contact the producer. 

Producer- Brennan Jones bjones89@msudenver.edu 

Production Title- The Cost of Greed 

Production Dates- Exact dates are not set but filming will be in October 

Logline- Peter and Henry are sent on a treasure hunt to a house that is believed to be abandoned. Where they then discover it's not a treasure hunt after all and they must face their greed. Either take the treasure or leave empty handed. 

Peter (19-25) Male 

Peter has a moral compass that he deals with during this film. He wants to do the right thing and in the end that pays off for him. 

Henry (19-25) Male 

Henry is a billionaire with no need for more money, however that does not stop him from thinking he needs more. He is corrupt and in the end karma gets to him. 

Audition Dates- September 18th-September 29th

Audition Location- Email-Self Tape

This is a student film for a final project therefore this film is non paid and non union.

Contact Email- bjones89@msudenver.edu 

Must contact the producer to be consider for the role. Once you contact Brennan he will send you the audition material.

items.text:
Hello, we are currently casting for a student film on Auraria Campus! 

Producers- Isabella Coronado & Alanagh Finken 

Production Title- Normal Activity 

Production Dates- We don't have exact dates yet but we do know that we are filming in October. 

Logline- A mocumentary following a college's ghost hunting group as they prepare to explore a haunted local brewery's basement where a spirit has resided for the past thirty years. 

Alex (19-25) Male 

Alex is the leader of the ghost hunting group, he is very enthusiastic. He is clearly the one that is most devoted to this group. 

Chelsea (19-25) Female 

Chelsea is your typical girly girl likes being on camera but does not care about the club she is in. She is pretending to so that the club can get funding for the "haunted (not haunted) hot springs". 

Tommy (19-25) Male 

Tommy is very clearly apart of the club because he has eyes for Chelsea, he could not care less otherwise. 

Vera (19-25) Female 

Vera is Alex's sister and is only there because Alex believes they needed a fourth member and basically bribed Vera to join by saying she could borrow his car whenever she wants. 

Gary (45-55) Male 

Gary is the nightwatchmen for the brewery basement. He is very encouraging to Alex with his ghost hunting group. However that encouragement is not for reasons you think, Gary has a secret. 

Documentarian (20-30) Male, Female, Non Binary 

The documentarian is not really shown on camera, however they play a very important role. They are the voice we hear throughout the film asking questions to our characters, and making sarcastic and humorous remarks because they like everyone except Alex, thinks this club is utterly ridicules. 

Audition Dates- September 18th-September 29th 

Audition Location- Email-Self Tape 

This is a student film for a final project therefore this film is non paid and non union. 

**Contact Email- afinken1@msudenver.edu | icoronad@msudenver.edu **

**You must email both producers. Email the producers about your interest in the role and then we will send you the audition piece for your self tape. You must email to be considered, Facebook Messages does not count. **

items.text:
INTENSE CRIME DRAMA - SHORT (PAID)

1-day shoot in London (UK) for 2nd week in October 2025 (date tbc)

(For actors based in the London area).

 

Summary: A night of heavy drinking ends in a deadly contest between newfound besties - a fearless Nigerian gangland enforcer and a trigger-happy European gunman.

 

This project is Episode #0 of ‘Brave Hunter in Ghost City’  - introducing a new African story world and some of its main characters. ** **

 

MALE LEAD: to play fearless gangland enforcer.  Black African, 25-45, Lagos accent, 5’6”+, athletic physique with good fitness and conditioning. Stage combat training. Flat rate of £300 for 15 hours.

 

MALE LEAD: to play trigger-happy gunman. White European,  35-45, 5’ 6”+, 85kg-100kg,  powerful physique with good fitness and conditioning. Stage combat training. Flat rate of £300 for 15 hours.

 

SUPPORTING MALE: to play dead gangster. White European, 35-45, 5’ 6”+, 80kg-100kg. Half a day of shooting for £150 for 7 hours.

 

You will need professional experience playing character roles on Stage, Film or TV. Please send in a cover letter, your CV with headshot and your showreel to Davina Brown at k2Filmworks@gmail.com

items.text:
**📣 Stellenausschreibung – TanzHaus Erfurt**

**Tanzpädagog:innen & Tanzlehrer:innen (m/w/d) gesucht**

**für verschiedene Tanzrichtungen – Festanstellung oder auf Honorarbasis**

**🕺 Über uns**

Das **TanzHaus Erfurt** ist eines der größten Tanzstudios in Thüringen mit rund 1000 Mitgliedern. Unser Programm umfasst ein breites Spektrum von **Hip Hop, Commercial, Urban Contemporary** über **Jazz, Modern Dance, Ballett** bis hin zu **Kindertanz, Fitness- und Paartanzkursen**. Mehrere Companies und Crews sind Teil unserer Schule.
Neben dem regulären Unterricht sind wir Gastgeber der **Internationalen Erfurter Sommertanztage** und kooperieren mit Dozent:innen aus aller Welt.

Zur Verstärkung unseres Teams suchen wir engagierte **Tanzlehrer:innen und Tanzpädagog:innen** für verschiedene Stilrichtungen.

**🎯 Dein Profil**
* Du unterrichtest einen oder mehrere Tanzstile (z. B. **Hip Hop, Commercial, Jazz, Contemporary, Ballett, Kindertanz**).
* Du hast Freude an der Arbeit mit verschiedenen Altersgruppen (Kinder, Jugendliche, Erwachsene) verschiedener Level (Anfänger bis Fortgeschrittene).
* Du verfügst über Unterrichtserfahrung oder eine pädagogische Ausbildung im Tanz.
* Du hast vielleicht Erfahrung bei der Entwicklung von Wettkampf-Choreografien.
* Du bist zuverlässig, teamorientiert und motiviert, **regelmäßig in Erfurt** zu unterrichten.

**💡 Wir bieten dir**
* **Mehrere feste Kurse pro Woche** – mit Option auf Ausbau.
* Möglichkeit einer **Festanstellung** (Vollzeit, Teilzeit, Midi- oder Minijob) oder attraktiver Honorartätigkeit.
* Eine moderne künstlerische Tanzschule mit professionell ausgestatteten Studios.
* Ein tolles Team, was dich mit offenen Armen empfängt.
* Eine lebendige Tanz-Community und Auftrittsmöglichkeiten bei Events & Projekten.
* Raum für deine Kreativität und Unterstützung bei der Umsetzung eigener Ideen.

**📍 Standort**

**TanzHaus Erfurt – im Herzen Thüringens, in der Mitte von Deutschland**
Zentrale Lage mit guter Erreichbarkeit (Leipzig, Halle, Jena, Weimar, Berlin, Frankfurt, Kassel, Hannover, Göttingen, Coburg, Bamberg, Nürnberg).

**📩 Bewerbung**

👉 Sende uns deine **kurze Vorstellung + Tanzvideo oder CV** an:
📧 info@tanzhaus-erfurt.de
☎️ 0176 41113147

Zur Verstärkung unseres Teams suchen wir engagierte **Tanzlehrer:innen und Tanzpädagog:innen** für verschiedene Stilrichtungen.

**🎯 Dein Profil**
* Du unterrichtest einen oder mehrere Tanzstile (z. B. **Hip Hop, Commercial, Jazz, Contemporary, Ballett, Kindertanz**).
* Du hast Freude an der Arbeit mit verschiedenen Altersgruppen (Kinder, Jugendliche, Erwachsene) verschiedener Level (Anfänger bis Fortgeschrittene).
* Du verfügst über Unterrichtserfahrung oder eine pädagogische Ausbildung im Tanz.
* Du hast vielleicht Erfahrung bei der Entwicklung von Wettkampf-Choreografien.
* Du bist zuverlässig, teamorientiert und motiviert, **regelmäßig in Erfurt** zu unterrichten.

**💡 Wir bieten dir**
* **Mehrere feste Kurse pro Woche** – mit Option auf Ausbau.
* Möglichkeit einer **Festanstellung** (Vollzeit, Teilzeit, Midi- oder Minijob) oder attraktiver Honorartätigkeit.
* Eine moderne künstlerische Tanzschule mit professionell ausgestatteten Studios.
* Ein tolles Team, was dich mit offenen Armen empfängt.
* Eine lebendige Tanz-Community und Auftrittsmöglichkeiten bei Events & Projekten.
* Raum für deine Kreativität und Unterstützung bei der Umsetzung eigener Ideen.

**📍 Standort**

**TanzHaus Erfurt – im Herzen Thüringens, in der Mitte von Deutschland**
Zentrale Lage mit guter Erreichbarkeit (Leipzig, Halle, Jena, Weimar, Berlin, Frankfurt, Kassel, Hannover, Göttingen, Coburg, Bamberg, Nürnberg).

**📩 Bewerbung**

👉 Sende uns deine **kurze Vorstellung + Tanzvideo oder CV** an:
📧 info@tanzhaus-erfurt.de
☎️ 0176 41113147

🌆 CAPE TOWN CBD CASTING CALL! 🎥
Street Party Vibes x Paid Shoot x Big Energy

🎬 Looking to start your acting journey? Let’s go!

👉 +27 68 499 9959
